---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="Saar Paamoni — Product leader, artist, surfer, builder, dad.">
    <article class="post-content no-image">
        <div class="post-content-body about-body">
            <h1 class="about-title">About</h1>

            <p class="about-lead">
                Product leader, artist, surfer, builder, dad —
                not necessarily in that order.
            </p>

            <p>
                I spent a decade as SVP Product @ DoubleVerify, where I led measurement
                and verification products across CTV, display, video, and mobile — at a scale
                of billions of signals per day. I've worked across the full ad ecosystem:
                DSPs, SSPs, publishers, agencies, and standards bodies (IAB, MRC). Many times, I know
                how to spot real opportunities that are being missed by others.
            </p>

            <p>
                Now I advise founders and operators building at the intersection of AI, media,
                and measurement — and I'm quietly building something of my own.
            </p>

            <h2>Making things</h2>
            <p>
                Outside of product work, I paint. Acrylic on canvas, mostly — bold,
                textured, warm. Painting is my way of thinking without language. It's
                what I do when I want to be fully present without an agenda.
            </p>
            <p>
                I also surf, badly and happily, whenever the opportunity arises.
            </p>

            <h2>Where I'm at</h2>
            <p>
                Based in Israel. Spending a lot of time thinking about how AI is
                reshaping how brands and publishers understand real audience engagement.
                More on that soon.
            </p>

            <div class="about-links">
                <a href="/consulting">Work with me →</a>
                <a href="/art">See my art →</a>
                <a href="/contact">Get in touch →</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </article>
</Layout>

<style>
.about-body {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem var(--margin);
}

.about-title {
    font-family: var(--font-sans-serif);
    font-variant: small-caps;
    font-weight: var(--font-light);
    font-size: 4rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--color-base);
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
}

.about-lead {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.about-body p {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-base);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.about-body h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-sans-serif);
    font-variant: small-caps;
    font-weight: var(--font-normal);
    font-size: 1.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin: 2.5rem 0 0.75rem;
    text-transform: lowercase;
}

.about-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
}

.about-links a {
    font-family: var(--font-sans-serif);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}

.about-links a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
}
</style>
